 	<p class="content-nav">
 	        <a href="http://blog.guykawasaki.com/2006/08/ten_questions_w_1.html">« Ten Questions with "Dr. Evil"</a> |
 	        <a href="http://blog.guykawasaki.com/">Main</a>
